title: Urbanization in Tanzania 2018
yAxis: Share of urban population in total population
summary: In general Share of urban population in total population has rose over the Year.
Share of urban population in total population is slightly increasing from 2011 to 2015.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2014 and 2015.
The highest Share of urban population in total population, of value 31.62 was reached at Year 2015
Minimum Share of urban population in total population about 28.8 was reached at Year 2011
